WEBVTT

00:00:01.503 --> 00:00:03.842
[NARRATOR] Last time
on Dragon Ball Z Kai:

00:00:04.042 --> 00:00:05.945
Sick of his cohort's
incompetence,

00:00:05.978 --> 00:00:08.584
Vegeta removed Nappa
from the battlefield...

00:00:08.617 --> 00:00:11.624
Then, as the fight between
Goku and Vegeta began...

00:00:11.657 --> 00:00:12.959
Goku quickly realized,

00:00:12.993 --> 00:00:16.232
his only hope of matching his
opponent's unbelievable power,

00:00:16.265 --> 00:00:19.038
was to push his
body to its limit.

00:00:19.071 --> 00:00:20.407
Will it pay off?

00:00:20.441 --> 00:00:25.250
Body, don't fail me now!
Kaio-ken times three!

