Hey it's me, Goku!

00:22:39.519 --> 00:22:41.455
Oh, man... I've gathered
enough energy from Earth

00:22:41.488 --> 00:22:42.657
to make a Spirit Bomb,

00:22:42.691 --> 00:22:44.828
but Vegeta's attack
was just too fast!

00:22:44.861 --> 00:22:46.197
I don't know if
I'll be able to...

00:22:46.231 --> 00:22:47.067
[VEGETA]
You should know by now

00:22:47.100 --> 00:22:48.302
that it won't work...

00:22:48.335 --> 00:22:50.339
not before I crush you
with my bare hands!

00:22:50.372 --> 00:22:52.677
[GOHAN] Stop it! Put
my dad down right now!

00:22:52.711 --> 00:22:53.813
[VEGETA] You little brat!

00:22:53.846 --> 00:22:55.383
I'll teach you to
go after my tail!

00:22:55.416 --> 00:22:58.121
[GOKU] Next time
on Dragon Ball Z Kai!

00:22:58.155 --> 00:22:59.558
"Goku on the Ropes!

00:22:59.591 --> 00:23:01.629
Pin Your Hopes on
the Spirit Bomb!"

00:23:01.662 --> 00:23:03.899
[GOHAN]
I will defeat you!

